title: [Boreas Meadows, Levantera Road]
description: A few cobbles are missing here and there, providing holes to trip up the unwary.  A chicken pecks industriously at one hole, apparently having found something of interest in it.  Daisies and asters line the road, providing a cheerful front to the homes along it.

The moon illuminates the street and shows a few cobbles missing here and there, providing holes to trip up the unwary.  Daisies and asters line the road, their bright colors still visible in the light from homes behind them.
